title: InChIKey
name: inchikey
description: Calculates Standard InChIKey

title: Stereo [Parent]
name: stereoParent
description: Stereo designations (R/S) of stereocenters for parent salt-stripped structure.

title: Stereocenter Count
name: stereoCount
description: Count of stereocenters in format <total sites>,<assigned sites>. For example, a structure with 1 possible stereocenter, where that center is undefined would return "1,0"

title: SMILES
name: smiles
description: Calculates SMILES representation for structure

title: Layered Hashes
name: hash
description: Calculates layered hash of structure.

title: Pubchem CID
name: cid
description: Pubchem CID for the structure, matched based on InChIKey.

title: ChEMBL
name: chembl
description: ChEMBL id for the structure, matched based on InChIKey.

title: Exact Molecular Mass
name: molExactMass
description: Calculates exact molecular mass

title: NCGC IDs
name: qhts
description: Get NCGC IDs for given structure

title: CNS score
name: cns
description: CNS penetration score based on physical properties

title: Hydrogen Bond Donors
name: hbd
description: Hydrogen Bond Donor Count at pH 3.0 using ChemAxon software

title: Hydrogen Bond Acceptors
name: hba
description: Hydrogen Bond Acceptor Count at pH 3.0 using ChemAxon software

title: TPSA
name: tpsa
description: Total Polar Surface Area

title: LogP
name: logp
description: LogP

title: LogD
name: logd
description: LogD

title: Rotatable Bonds
name: rbc
description: Count of rotatable bonds

title: SSSR Count
name: sssr
description: SSSR Count

title: Lead-like Violations
name: lead
description: Lead-like filter violations. Returns the violations of the lead-like filter.

title: Drug-like Violations
name: drug
description: Drug-like filter violations. Returns the violations of the drug-like filter.

title: Most Basic pKa
name: mbpka
description: Most Basic pKa (highest pH at which molecule will be positively charged 50% of the time)

title: Lychi
name: lychi
description: Calculates Lychi 4-layer hash of structure.

title: Lychi [Parent]
name: lychiParent
description: Calculates Lychi 4-layer hash of structure after selecting the largest disconnected moiety (salt-stripping).

title: Lychi Layer 1
name: lychi1
description: Lychi Layer 1 (atom insensitive)

title: Lychi Layer 2
name: lychi2
description: Lychi Layer 2 (bond insensitive)

title: Lychi Layer 3
name: lychi3
description: Lychi Layer 3 (stereo insensitive)

title: Lychi Layer 4
name: lychi4
description: Lychi Layer 4 (stereo sensitive)

title: PAINS Filters
name: pains
description: Calculates any patterns that are PAINS problems

title: Exact Molecular Mass [Parent]
name: molExactMassParent
description: Calculates exact molecular mass for parent salt-stripped structure.

title: Molecular Formula [Parent]
name: molFormParent
description: Calculates Molecular Formula for parent salt-stripped structure.

title: Molecular Formula
name: molForm
description: Calculates Molecular Formula

title: Molecular Weight
name: molWeight
description: Calculates Molecular Weight

title: Molecular Weight [Parent]
name: molWeightParent
description: Calculates Molecular Weight for parent salt-stripped structure.

title: SMILES [Parent]
name: smilesParent
description: Calculates SMILES representation for parent salt-stripped structure.

title: Salt SMILES
name: smallestMoietySmiles
description: Calculates SMILES for the smallest disconnected fragment (sometimes called a moiety by convention).

title: Salt Name
name: smallestMoietyName
description: Calculates name for the smallest disconnected fragment (sometimes called a moiety by convention). This is meant to be the 'salt' name.

title: Salt Count
name: smallestMoietyCount
description: Calculates number of repeats for the smallest disconnected fragment (sometimes called a moiety by convention). This is usually the same as the 'salt' count.

title: Image URL
name: img
description: Calculates a URL for viewing an image of the structure.

title: NCATS Predictor Target
name: predictorTarget
description: Returns the best predicted target and -Log(IC50) using NCATS Predictor.

title: NCATS Predictor Models
name: predictor
description: Returns applicable NCATS Predictor models and their predicted values for a supplied structure.

title: Tautomers
name: tautomers
description: Calculates tautomers for given structure.

title: FASTMAP Embedding
name: fastmap
description: Embed structures into n-dimensional space using fastmap algorithm

title: FDA UNII Code
name: unii
description: Lookup UNII code from FDA sources.

title: Highest Development Phase
name: devphase
description: Fetch highest development phase from Inxight Drugs

title: Substance Description
name: description
description: Fetch description of substance from stitcher

title: Substance primary MOA
name: moa
description: Fetch primary MOA of substance from stitcher

title: DrugBank primary MOA
name: drugbankmoa
description: Fetch DrugBank-annotated MOA of substance from stitcher

title: NPC primary MOA
name: npcmoa
description: Fetch NPC-annotated MOA of substance from stitcher

title: Target geneIDs
name: stitch_target
description: GeneID stitcher target

title: Target (Human) geneIDs
name: stitch_target_human
description: GeneID stitcher human target

title: Primary Targets
name: ptargets
description: Fetch primary target IDs for a compound

title: SP3 Carbon Fraction
name: sp3f
description: Fraction (from 0 to 1) of carbons which are in SP3 hybridization state. If 0 carbons, returns 0.

title: SP3/(SP3+SP2) Carbon Fraction
name: sp3sp2f
description: Fraction (from 0 to 1) of carbon atoms found in SP3 among all sp2+sp3 carbons.

title: CAS Registry Number
name: cas
description: CAS registry number as obtained from FDA GSRS records.

title: Preferred Term (FDA)
name: pt
description: FDA GSRS preferred term for substance record.

title: Names (FDA)
name: names
description: FDA GSRS list of names for record.

title: Set Lookup:DEA
name: dea
description: Lookup structure in 'DEA' set

title: Set Lookup:DEA[URL]
name: dea(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'DEA' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:TORONTO
name: toronto
description: Lookup structure in 'TORONTO' set

title: Set Lookup:TORONTO[URL]
name: toronto(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'TORONTO' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:TOCRIS
name: tocris
description: Lookup structure in 'TOCRIS' set

title: Set Lookup:TOCRIS[URL]
name: tocris(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'TOCRIS' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:AXON
name: axon
description: Lookup structure in 'AXON' set

title: Set Lookup:AXON[URL]
name: axon(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'AXON' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:DEA_SCHED
name: dea_sched
description: Lookup structure in 'DEA_SCHED' set

title: Set Lookup:DEA_SCHED[URL]
name: dea_sched(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'DEA_SCHED' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:SANTA_CRUZ
name: santa_cruz
description: Lookup structure in 'SANTA_CRUZ' set

title: Set Lookup:SANTA_CRUZ[URL]
name: santa_cruz(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'SANTA_CRUZ' set, returns URL

title: Set Lookup:SELLECK
name: selleck
description: Lookup structure in 'SELLECK' set

title: Set Lookup:SELLECK[URL]
name: selleck(URL)
description: Lookup structure in 'SELLECK' set, returns URL
